    "description": "Manufactured OpenAPI artifact for Plaid API. This file was synthesized by Last Mile from curated research JSON and is not vendor-certified. Use it as an agent-consumable starting point, then validate paths, schemas, authentication, and server URLs with the vendor before production use. Plaid's public API reference documents JSON-over-HTTP endpoints served from sandbox and production environments, and its public plaid-openapi repository exposes a dated raw OpenAPI definition. The public docs cover Link token creation, accounts, transactions sync, identity, auth, liabilities, investment transactions, processor token creation, transfer flows, payment initiation, asset report creation and retrieval, and webhooks. This is a strong write-capable open finance platform, but it does not represent asset or telemetry data. Asset data is Unsupported. Telemetry data is Unsupported. Writeback is Supported.",
